Package TextEditor

package TextEditor
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    Command
    Command interface implemented by the concrete command classes Extended by the Recordable interface
    Engine
    Main API for the text editing engine
    Invoker
    Invoker interface implemented by the InvokerImpl
    Memento
    Empty Memento interface implemented by the specific memento classes
    Originator
    Originator interface implemented by the concrete command classes Extended by the Recordable interface
    Recordable
    Recordable interface that extends the Command and Originator interfaces
    Selection
    Provides access to selection control operations
